            <title>[HBASE-9481] Servershutdown handler get aborted with ConcurrentModificationException</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-9481</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In integration tests, we found SSH got aborted with following stack trace:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
